Commander, information as requested...
 COMMAND HELP
= refit command =

Ship skins and projectiles for specific ships

Command ::
!refit

Aliases ::
!skin !projectile
Syntax:
!refit <name> <filters>

Name ::
 * Full/partial/nickname ship/skin/projectile name

Filters ::
 * faction   - neutral, federation, romulan, klingon
 * grade     - G3 to G4 / 3* to 4*
 * rarity    - rare, epic
 * type      - interceptor, explorer, battleship
Usage Examples:
!refit                 = detailed list of skins & projectiles
!skins                 = detailed list of skins
!g3 skins              = g3 ship skins
!fed skins             = federation ship skins
!exp skins             = explorer ship skins
!projectiles           = detailed list of projectiles
!refit augur           = skin(s) for Augur
!augur skin            = skin(s) for Augur
!constellation skin    = skin(s) for ISS Jellyfish
!refit fusion          = fusion beam projectile
!fusion projectile     = fusion beam projectile
Notes:
 * Faction name: neu fed kli rom
 * Ship types: int, exp, bshp

